high_descs: Turn right to reach the countertop.
Pick up the knife from the microwave.
Turn left to reach the bread.
Cut the bread in the sink into pieces with the knife.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of bread from the sink.
Turn right to reach the microwave.
Heat the bread slice in the microwave and take the bread out.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Put the slice of bread in the top of the fridge with the other bread.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread in the Fridge.

high_descs: turn around and walk across the room to the countertop.
go to the microwave and take out the knife from inside of it.
walk over to the bread in the sink.
Slice the bread into pieces.
Put the knife under the sink.
Take a slice of bread from the loaf.
go to the microwave and put the bread in the microwave.
take the bread from the microwave.
walk over to the fridge with the bread.
Put the bread from the fridge in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Getting the bread from the fridge to another place.

high_descs: Turn around, turn left. Approach the countertop.
Open the microwave. Take out the knife. Close the microwave.
Turn to the left. Continue to the bread. Turn right.
Open the left door of the sink cabinet. Cut the bread into slices.
Place the knife on the bread on the sink.
Take a slice of bread and close the cabinet door.
Turn right. Go to the microwave. Turn left.
Open the door to the microwave. Place the slice of bread on the left side vertically. Close the door. Turn on the microwave for 5 seconds. Open the door. Take out the bread. Close the door.
Turn around. Go forward to the fridge. Turn right, approaching the fridge.
Turn around. Keep going, get to the fridge. Turn right. Approach the fridge. Open the doors. Place the bread slice vertically on the first level on the left side. Close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Find a slice of Bread, place it in the Fridge.
